text: Jai Surya High School is a school in Vijay Nagar Urban Estate, Jind, Haryana, India. Established in year 1998, Jai Surya High School is a co-educational day school. The foundation stone of the school building was laid in 1997. ==See also== *Education in India *Literacy in India *List of institutions of higher education in Haryana ==References== ==External links== Category:High schools and secondary schools in Haryana Category:Jind district
